TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed Keys extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定按鍵碼 (Key Code) 和修飾詞 (Modifier)。

remarks.format: ## Remarks 類別包含常數，用來處理鍵盤輸入。The class contains constants for processing keyboard input. 索引鍵的列舉型別的成員是由按鍵碼和修飾詞組合成一個整數值的一組所組成。The members of the Keys enumeration consist of a key code and a set of modifiers combined into a single integer value. 在 Win32 應用程式開發介面 (API) 的索引鍵的值有兩個部分，包含關鍵程式碼 （這是與 Windows 的虛擬按鍵碼相同），高序位位元與表示索引鍵的修飾詞，例如 SHIFT、 控制和 alt 鍵的低序位位元索引鍵。In the Win32 application programming interface (API) a key value has two halves, with the high-order bits containing the key code (which is the same as a Windows virtual key code), and the low-order bits representing key modifiers such as the SHIFT, CONTROL, and ALT keys. > [!WARNING] > 請勿結合的位元運算中使用此列舉中值。Do not use the values in this enumeration for combined bitwise operations. 列舉中的值不會互斥。The values in the enumeration are not mutually exclusive. > [!NOTE] > 此列舉會提供任何方法來測試是否目前已啟動下 CAPS LOCK 或 NUM LOCK 鍵。This enumeration provides no way to test whether the CAPS LOCK or NUM LOCK keys are currently activated. 您可以使用下列技巧來判斷是否要啟動這些按鍵：You can use one of the following techniques to determine if these keys are activated: - 請呼叫 類別的 方法。Call the method of the class. - 進行更細微的控制，請使用 Win32 API 函式`GetKeyState`， `GetAsyncKeyState`，或`GetKeyboardState`user32.dll，若要這樣做中定義。For finer control, use the Win32 API functions `GetKeyState`, `GetAsyncKeyState`, or `GetKeyboardState` defined in user32.dll, to do this. 如需呼叫原生函式的詳細資訊，請參閱[使用 Unmanaged DLL 函式](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md)。For more information about calling native functions, see [Consuming Unmanaged DLL Functions](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md). 下表顯示兩個列舉值，表示一般的原始設備製造商 (OEM) 索引鍵和更具體的美式鍵盤關聯所代表之索引鍵的程式碼值。The following table shows the key code values represented by two enumerated values, representing both the general original equipment manufacturer (OEM) keys and the more specific U.S.-keyboard associations. |十六進位值Hexadecimal value|美式鍵盤U.S. keyboard|一般的 OEMGeneral OEM| |-----------------------|-------------------|-----------------| |BABA|OemSemicolonOemSemicolon|Oem1Oem1| |BFBF|OemQuestionOemQuestion|Oem2Oem2| |C0C0|OemtildeOemtilde|Oem3Oem3| |DBDB|OemOpenBracketsOemOpenBrackets|Oem4Oem4| |DCDC|OemPipeOemPipe|Oem5Oem5| |DDDD|OemCloseBracketsOemCloseBrackets|Oem6Oem6| |DEDE|OemQuotesOemQuotes|Oem7Oem7| |E2E2|OemBackslashOemBackslash|Oem102Oem102| > [!CAUTION] > 針對.NET Framework 2.0 中，成員 IMEAccept 已加入，會取代先前的項目 IMEAceept，拼字不正確。For the .NET Framework 2.0, a member IMEAccept was added that supersedes the previous entry, IMEAceept, which was spelled incorrectly. 回溯相容性，已保留較舊的版本，但它可能在未來版本的.NET framework 中刪除The older version has been retained for backward compatibility, but it may be deleted in future versions of the .NET Framework ## Examples 下列程式碼範例使用事件，以判斷輸入控制項的字元類型。The following code example uses the event to determine the type of character entered into the control.
